OL,6,FReferee David Coote has been sacked
OL,7,Fafter an expletive-filled video
OL,8,Femerged showing him making derogatory
OL,9,Fcomments about former Liverpool
OL,10,Fmanager Jurgen Klopp.
OL,12,FProfessional Game Match Officials
OL,13,FLimited (PGMOL) confirmed the
OL,14,Ftermination of the 42-year-old
OL,15,FNottinghamshire official's employment
OL,16,Fin a statement on Monday 9 December.
