OL,3,CReferee David Coote sacked after
OL,4,CJurgen Klopp comments
OL,6,FCoote was suspended by PGMOL after the
OL,7,Fvideo first emerged on 11 November and
OL,8,Fwas shared widely across social media.
OL,10,FIn the video he calls Klopp a "German
OL,11,F****" and "f***ing arrogant", as well
OL,12,Fas criticising Liverpool saying
OL,13,F"Liverpool were s**t".
OL,15,FHe then uses an offensive term to
OL,16,Fdescribe Klopp and, asked why he felt
OL,17,Fthat way about the German, Coote says
OL,18,Fhe had "a right pop at me when I
OL,19,Freffed them against Burnley in
OL,20,Flockdown" and "accused me of lying".
