OL,6,FThe investigation by PGMOL which led
OL,7,Fto Coote's contract being terminated
OL,8,Fis also understood to have looked at
OL,9,Fanother video which appeared to show
OL,10,FCoote snorting a white powder,
OL,11,Fpurportedly during Euro 2024 where he
OL,12,Fwas one of the assistant VARs for the
OL,13,Ftournament.
OL,15,FEuropean football's governing body
OL,16,FUEFA also appointed an ethics
OL,17,Finvestigator to look into the matter.
