OL,6,FThe FA is also separately
OL,7,Finvestigating an allegation `
OL,8,Fstrenuously denied by Coote - that he
OL,9,Fdiscussed the prospect of giving a
OL,10,FLeeds player a yellow card with a fan
OL,11,Fprior to a match in an online
OL,12,Fconversation.
OL,14,FThe Sun alleges after Coote booked the
OL,15,Fplayer, he messaged the individual
OL,16,Fback to say: "I hope you backed as
OL,17,Fdiscussed."
OL,19,FThe FA said it was investigating the
OL,20,Fallegation as "a matter of urgency".
