OL,6,FCoote said: "I strongly refute these
OL,7,Ffalse and defamatory allegations.
OL,8,FWhatever issues I may have had in my
OL,9,Fpersonal life, they have never
OL,10,Faffected my decision-making on the
OL,11,Ffield.
OL,13,F"I have always held the integrity of
OL,14,Fthe game in the highest regard,
OL,15,Frefereeing matches impartially and to
OL,16,Fthe best of my ability."
OL,18,FPGMOL's investigation did not look at
OL,19,Fthe allegation related to the Leeds
OL,20,Fyellow card.
